text: Video shows Biden's assistant being arrested
Photo shows Biden’s executive assistant being arrested for spying on Donald Trump
A post shared on Facebook purports President Joe Biden’s White House Chief of Staff Ron Klain was arrested by the U.S. Special Forces for crimes regarding the 2020 presidential election.
An arrest warrant has been issued for U.S. President-elect Joe Biden.
